{
    "swagger": "2.0",
    "info": {
        "version": "1.0",
        "title": "Plus Command API",
        "description": "Detayl\u0131 ve Pazaryeri sipari\u015fleri olu\u015fturan, sipari\u015f teslimat\u0131n\u0131 iptal eden, al\u0131c\u0131 olu\u015fturan, g\u00f6nderi teslimant problemlerine yan\u0131t veren metodlar\u0131n yer ald\u0131\u011f\u0131 API'd\u0131r. | It is the API that creates Detailed Order and Market Place Order, cancels order delivery, create recipient, answers shipment delivery problems.",
        "termsOfService": "http://swagger.io/terms/"
    },
    "basePath": "/mngapi/api/pluscmdapi",
    "paths": {
        "/createDetailedOrder": {
            "post": {
                "tags": [
                    "PlusCommand"
                ],
                "summary": "Create Detailed Order",
                "description": "'Detayl\u0131' sipari\u015f olu\u015fturur. Al\u0131c\u0131 ve g\u00f6nderici bilgisi de\u011ferleri doldurulurken ya CustomerId verilir ya da Al\u0131c\u0131 ve G\u00f6nderici'nin FullName, CityCode, DistrictCode, Address alanlar\u0131 ve MobilePhoneNumber, HomePhoneNumber, BussinessPhoneNumber' dan herhangi biri girilmelidir. | Creates detailed type of order. When you fill Recipient, Shipper areas either you set CustomerId or Recipient's and Shipper's FullName, CityCode, DistrictCode, Address and one of the MobilePhoneNumber, HomePhoneNumber, BussinessPhoneNumber.",
                "operationId": "CreateDetailedOrderPost",
                "consumes": [
                    "application/json-patch+json",
                    "application/json",
                    "text/json",
                    "application/*+json"
                ],
                "produces": [
                    "application/json"
                ],
                "parameters": [
                    {
                        "name": "createDetailedOrderRequest",
                        "in": "body",
                        "required": false,
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/CreateDetailedOrderRequest"
                        }
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "x-api-version",
                        "in": "header",
                        "required": false,
                        "type": "string"
                    },
                    {
                        "name": "Authorization",
                        "in": "header",
                        "description": "JWT Authorization header using the Bearer scheme. Example: \"Authorization: Bearer {token}\"",
                        "required": true,
                        "type": "string"
                    }
                ],
                "responses": {
                    "200": {
                        "description": "Detailed order created",
                        "schema": {
                            "$ref": "#/definitions/CreateDetailedOrderResponse"
                        },
                        "examples": {
                            "application/json": {
                                "orderInvoiceId": "456764543",
                                "orderInvoiceDetailId": "25423565",
                                "shipperBranchCode": "1345"
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    "400": {
                        "description": "Bad Request"
                    },
                    "401": {
                        "description": "Unauthorized"
                    },
                    "500": {
                        "description": "Server Error"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
